## 封装加载图片的promise  
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
    })
}
```

student_answer:
let loadImg = (src)=>{
            return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
                let img = new Image();
                img.src=src
                img.onload =function(){
                    resolve(img)
                }
            })
        }
        loadImg('http://www.pptbz.com/pptpic/UploadFiles_6909/201203/2012031220155.jpg').then((res)=>{
            document.body.appendChild(res)
        })
